name: My void
description:
This is my portal, my darkness, my void.  When I go through the gates everything goes quiet. Not a word in my head, no whispers.. 
The dark force takes over my whole body. 
it's like a black void, where nothing can touch me, scare me or control me.. 
This is darkness I can not explain, you have to experience it with me.  You are welcome to.
